name: Sate Ikan Laut

review 1: One of the best meals I have had in my life. Such a small, unassuming little spot on the side of the road in the middle of a beautiful area. If you are anywhere close, please make sure to stop here for a meal. The sate was so good and the meatball soup was so amazing that I took an entire order too go after I ate a full meal! They were so reasonably prices for what they offer. Mekan sedap!!!
